<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>خ ل ع<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[١٦٦٩ - خ ل ع]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>خالعَ يُخالع، مُخالَعَةً، فهو مُخالِع، والمفعول مُخالَع<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• خالعتِ المرأةُ زوجهَا:</span> طلبت طلاقها بِبَذْلٍ من مالها<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>⦗٦٨٣⦘ تؤدّيه إليه.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">• خالع امرأتَه:</span> طلَّقها نظير مال تبذله له.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">• خالع فلانًا:</span> مازحه، داعبه.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>